title: Gotham S01 Soundtrack Selections
description:
Gotham.S01.Soundtrack.Selections

30 tracks from Gotham Season 1 including all of the rock, pop, punk, disco, alternative, and metal. Other music was used in the series, but oldies and classical tracks clash with the modern stuff. Each track was ripped from the web as a wave, encoded to mp3 224Kbps with the highest quality settings, and normalized to 90.3db. 

Naming format:
Gotham Episode - Performer - Title [author if not Performer] (optional note).mp3
